entities.description: primitive blocks are defined as a sequence of triplets representing components in a layout based model
title is listed as an initial layout based type for a primitive block
text is listed as an initial layout based type for a primitive block
table is listed as an initial layout based type for a primitive block
image is listed as an initial layout based type for a primitive block
fontsize is a layout feature associated with a primitive block

relations.description: title is one of the layout based types that can be assigned to a primitive block
text is one of the layout based types that can be assigned to a primitive block
table is one of the layout based types that can be assigned to a primitive block
image is one of the layout based types that can be assigned to a primitive block
fontsize is a layout feature that is part of the vector associated with a primitive block
